(1, 'Images/1917.jpg', 'Movies/1917_2019.mp4', '1917', 'April 6th, 1917. As a regiment assembles to wage war deep in enemy territory, two soldiers are assigned to race against time and deliver a message that will stop 1,600 men from walking straight into a deadly trap', 'Drama / War', 2019),
