(4, 'Images/300RiseOfAnEmpire.jpg', 'Movies/300RiseOfAnEmpire_2014.mp4', '300 Rise Of An Empire', 'Greek general Themistokles leads the charge against invading Persian forces led by mortal-turned-god Xerxes and Artemisia, vengeful commander of the Persian navy.', 'Action / Drama', 2014),
(5, 'Images/300.jpg', 'Movies/300_2006.mp4', '300', 'King Leonidas of Sparta and a force of 300 men fight the Persians at Thermopylae in 480 B.C.', 'Action / Drama', 2006),
(6, 'Images/30DaysOfNight.jpg', 'Movies/30DaysOfNight_2007.mp4', '30 Days Of Night', 'After an Alaskan town is plunged into darkness for a month, it is attacked by a bloodthirsty gang of vampires.', 'Action / Horror / Thriller', 2007),
(7, 'Images/5050.jpg', 'Movies/5050_2011.mp4', '5050', 'Inspired by a true story, a comedy centred on a 27-year-old guy who learns of his cancer diagnosis and his subsequent struggle to beat the disease.', 'Comedy / Drama / Romance', 2011),
(8, 'Images/63Up.jpg', 'Movies/63Up_2019.mp4', '63 Up', 'Director Michael Apted revisits the same group of British-born adults after a 7-year wait. The subjects are interviewed as to the changes that have occurred in their lives during the last seven years.', 'Documentary', 2019),
(9, 'Images/AWoman.jpg', 'Movies/AWoman_2010.mp4', 'A Woman', 'A young woman falls in love with a famous novelist and travels with him to his home in Southern Italy. There, her obsession with the memory of his dead wife begins to consume her.', 'Drama', 2010),
(10, 'Images/Abominable.jpg', 'Movies/Abominable_2019.mp4', 'Abominable', 'Three teenagers must help a Yeti return to his family while avoiding a wealthy man and a zoologist who want him for their own needs. ', 'Adventure / Comedy / Family', 2019),
(11, 'Images/AboutTime.jpg', 'Movies/AboutTime_2013.mp4', 'About Time', 'At the age of 21, Tim discovers he can travel in time and change what happens and has happened in his own life. His decision to make his world a better place by getting a girlfriend turns out not to be as easy as you might think. ', 'Comedy / Drama / Fantasy', 2013),
(12, 'Images/AceVenturaPetDetective.jpg', 'Movies/AceVenturaPetDetective_1994.mp4', 'Ace Ventura Pet Detective', 'A goofy detective specializing in animals goes in search of the missing mascot of the Miami Dolphins. ', 'Comedy', 1994),
(13, 'Images/AceVenturaWhenNatureCalls.jpg', 'Movies/AceVenturaWhenNatureCalls_1995.mp4', 'Ace Ventura When Nature Calls', 'Ace Ventura, Pet Detective, returns from a spiritual quest to investigate the disappearance of a rare white bat, the sacred animal of a tribe in Africa. ', 'Adventure / Comedy / Crime', 1995),
(14, 'Images/AdAstra.jpg', 'Movies/AdAstra_2019.mp4', 'Ad Astra', 'Astronaut Roy McBride undertakes a mission across an unforgiving solar system to uncover the truth about his missing father and his doomed expedition that now, 30 years later, threatens the universe.', 'Adventure / Drama / Mystery', 2019),
(15, 'Images/AlitaBattleAngel.jpg', 'Movies/AlitaBattleAngel_2019.mp4', 'Alita Battle Angel', 'A deactivated cyborg is revived, but can&#39;t remember anything of her past and goes on a quest to find out who she is.', 'Action / Adventure / Sci-Fi', 2019),
(16, 'Images/AnAdventureInSpaceAndTime.jpg', 'Movies/AnAdventureInSpaceAndTime_2013.mp4', 'An Adventure In Space And Time', 'A dramatisation of the early years of Doctor Who (1963), with the story revolving around BBC executive Sydney Newman, novice producer Verity Lambert and actor William Hartnell. ', 'Biography / Drama / History', 2013),
(17, 'Images/Apollo11.jpg', 'Movies/Apollo11_2019.mp4', 'Apollo 11', 'A look at the Apollo 11 mission to land on the moon led by commander Neil Armstrong and pilots Buzz Aldrin and Michael Collins. ', 'Documentary / History', 2019),
(18, 'Images/Argo.jpg', 'Movies/Argo_2012.mp4', 'Argo', 'Acting under the cover of a Hollywood producer scouting a location for a science fiction film, a CIA agent launches a dangerous operation to rescue six Americans in Tehran during the U.S. hostage crisis in Iran in 1979. ', 'Biography / Drama / Thriller', 2012),
(19, 'Images/AssassinsCreed.jpg', 'Movies/AssassinsCreed_2016.mp4', 'Assassins Creed', 'Callum Lynch explores the memories of his ancestor Aguilar de Nerha and gains the skills of a Master Assassin, before taking on the secret Templar society.', 'Action / Adventure / Sci-Fi', 2016),
(20, 'Images/BackToTheFuturePart2.jpg', 'Movies/BackToTheFuturePart2_1989.mp4', 'Back To The Future Part 2', 'After visiting 2015, Marty McFly must repeat his visit to 1955 to prevent disastrous changes to 1985...without interfering with his first trip. ', 'Adventure / Comedy / Sci-Fi', 1989),
(21, 'Images/BackToTheFuturePart3.jpg', 'Movies/BackToTheFuturePart3_1990.mp4', 'Back To The Future Part 3', 'Stranded in 1955, Marty McFly learns about the death of Doc Brown in 1885 and must travel back in time to save him. With no fuel readily available for the DeLorean, the two must figure how to escape the Old West before Emmett is murdered.', 'Adventure / Comedy / Sci-Fi', 1990),
(22, 'Images/BackToTheFuture.jpg', 'Movies/BackToTheFuture_1985.mp4', 'Back To The Future', 'Marty McFly, a 17-year-old high school student, is accidentally sent thirty years into the past in a time-travelling DeLorean invented by his close friend, the eccentric scientist Doc Brown.', 'Adventure / Comedy / Sci-Fi', 1985),
(23, 'Images/BadBoysForLife.jpg', 'Movies/BadBoysForLife_2020.mp4', 'Bad Boys For Life', 'Miami detectives Mike Lowrey and Marcus Burnett must face off against a mother-and-son pair of drug lords who wreak vengeful havoc on their city. ', 'Action / Comedy', 2020),
(24, 'Images/Birdman.jpg', 'Movies/Birdman_2014.mp4', 'Birdman', 'A washed-up superhero actor attempts to revive his fading career by writing, directing, and starring in a Broadway production. ', 'Comedy / Drama', 2014),
(25, 'Images/BlackAndBlue.jpg', 'Movies/BlackAndBlue_2019.mp4', 'Black And Blue', 'A rookie New Orleans police officer is forced to balance her identity as a black woman after she witnesses two corrupt cops committing murder. ', 'Action / Crime / Thriller', 2019),
(26, 'Images/BlackSwan.jpg', 'Movies/BlackSwan_2010.mkv', 'Black Swan', 'A committed dancer struggles to maintain her sanity after winning the lead role in a production of Tchaikovsky&#39;s &#34;Swan Lake&#34;. ', 'Drama / Thriller', 2010),
(27, 'Images/Bloodshot.jpg', 'Movies/Bloodshot_2020.mp4', 'Bloodshot', 'Ray Garrison, an elite soldier who was killed in battle, is brought back to life by an advanced technology that gives him the ability of super human strength and fast healing. With his new abilities, he goes after the man who killed his wife, or at least, who he believes killed his wife. He soon comes to learn that not everything he learns can be trusted. The true question is: Can he even trust himself?', 'Action / Drama / Sci-Fi', 2020),
(28, 'Images/Bombshell.jpg', 'Movies/Bombshell_2019.mp4', 'Bombshell', 'A group of women take on Fox News head Roger Ailes and the toxic atmosphere he presided over at the network.', 'Biography / Drama', 2019),
(29, 'Images/Brexit.jpg', 'Movies/Brexit_2019.mp4', 'Brexit', 'Political strategist Dominic Cummings leads a popular but controversial campaign to convince British voters to leave the European Union from 2015 up until the present day.', 'Biography / Drama / History', 2019),
(30, 'Images/CabinFever.jpg', 'Movies/CabinFever_2002.mp4', 'Cabin Fever', 'Five college graduates rent a cabin in the woods and begin to fall victim to a horrifying flesh-eating virus, which attracts the unwanted attention of the homicidal locals.', 'Drama / Horror', 2002),
(31, 'Images/CabinFever2016.jpg', 'Movies/CabinFever_2016.mp4', 'Cabin Fever', 'While visiting their getaway cabin, five friends succumb to a flesh-eating disease.', 'Horror / Sci-Fi / Thriller', 2016),
(32, 'Images/CaptainPhillips.jpg', 'Movies/CaptainPhillips_2013.mp4', 'Captain Phillips', 'The true story of Captain Richard Phillips and the 2009 hijacking by Somali pirates of the U.S.-flagged MV Maersk Alabama, the first American cargo ship to be hijacked in two hundred years.', 'Adventure / Biography / Crime', 2013),
(33, 'Images/CloudAtlas.jpg', 'Movies/CloudAtlas_2012.mp4', 'Cloud Atlas', 'An exploration of how the actions of individual lives impact one another in the past, present and future, as one soul is shaped from a killer into a hero, and an act of kindness ripples across centuries to inspire a revolution. ', 'Action / Drama / Mystery', 2012),
(34, 'Images/ConAir.jpg', 'Movies/ConAir_1997.mp4', 'Con Air', 'Newly paroled ex-con and former U.S. Ranger Cameron Poe find himself trapped in a prisoner transport plane when the passengers seize control.', 'Action / Crime / Thriller', 1997),
(35, 'Images/ConsoleWars.jpg', 'Movies/ConsoleWars_2020.mp4', 'Console Wars', 'In 1990, SEGA, a fledgling arcade company assembled a team of misfits to take on the greatest video game company in the world, Nintendo. It was a once-in-a-lifetime, no-holds-barred conflict that pit brother against brother, kids against grownups, Sonic against Mario, and uniquely American capitalism against centuries-old Japanese tradition. For the first time ever, the men and women who fought on the front lines for Sega and Nintendo discuss this battle that defined a generation.', 'Documentary', 2020),
(36, 'Images/Coriolanus.jpg', 'Movies/Coriolanus_2011.mp4', 'Coriolanus', 'A banished hero of Rome allies with a sworn enemy to take his revenge on the city.', 'Drama / Thriller / War', 2011),
