(38, 'Images/X-menDarkPhoenix_2019.jpg', 'Movies/DarkPhoenix_2019.mp4', 'X-Men Dark Phoenix', 'Jean Grey begins to develop incredible powers that corrupt and turn her into a Dark Phoenix, causing the X-Men to decide if her life is worth more than all of humanity. ', 'Action / Adventure / Sci-Fi / Marvel', 2019),
