(42, 'Images/BatmanBegins.jpg', 'Movies/BatmanBegins_2005.mp4', 'Batman Begins', 'After training with his mentor, Batman begins his fight to free crime-ridden Gotham City from corruption. ', 'Action / Adventure / DC', 2005),
(43, 'Images/BatmanForever.jpg', 'Movies/BatmanForever_1995.mp4', 'Batman Forever', 'Batman must battle former district attorney Harvey Dent, who is now Two-Face and Edward Nygma, The Riddler with help from an amorous psychologist and a young circus acrobat who becomes his sidekick, Robin.', 'Action / Adventure / DC', 1995),
(44, 'Images/BatmanTheDarkKnight.jpg', 'Movies/BatmanTheDarkKnight_2008.mp4', 'Batman The Dark Knight', 'When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice. ', 'Action / Crime / DC / Drama', 2008),
