(46, 'Images/Batman.jpg', 'Movies/Batman_1989.mp4', 'Batman', 'The Dark Knight of Gotham City begins his war on crime with his first major enemy being Jack Napier, a criminal who becomes the clownishly homicidal Joker.', 'Action / Adventure / DC', 1989),
